PKG_SHORTDESC="Enlightenment Foundation Libraries (EFL)"
PKG_LONGDESC="Enlightenment Foundation Libraries (EFL)
These provide both a semi-traditional toolkit set in Elementary as well as the object canvas (Evas) and powerful abstracted objects (Edje) that you can combine, mix and match, even layer on top of each other with alpha channels and events in-tact."
